{"tid":171393,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"喜歡你讓我下沉","createTime":"2017-03-25T09:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T00:53:25.000Z","uid":13738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf6fe27db7ad1957f47c704b5af8f8fefd00796","tid":171393,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:46:05.000Z","msg":"兩個人偶然遇上<br />\n係天意定係一個陷阱<br />\n呢種曖曖昧昧既氣氛<br />\n係好甜既<br />\n我覺得已經一次又一次咁觸碰到佢內心最底個層<br />\n同樣我第一次感受到好似被接納被明白既感覺<br />\n可惜時間不對,人物不對,種種不對之下<br />\n但我已經沉左,迷失左<br />\n認真過,投入過,宜家應該要清醒<br />\n再唔醒,就可能番唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n講到1999,因為我都唔知自己做乜柒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> any肥,各位繼續努力搵明白自己既人,同時要珍惜有人明自己"},{"pid":"f18764ca078492f8c951e50937b87de35e85738f","tid":171393,"uid":69791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e89774bd66c6fcdb610515dd48f9209e8cec4da1","tid":171393,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"第一次拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1785adaa1165f9969a6dc85b37229a11e0794e4","tid":171393,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"尋愛侶消愁再沒畏懼每一夜<br />\n憑熱吻他人的嘴  蓋掩心碎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4a3bd23d221175c1fed58459d809355d186ddb","tid":171393,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉 假既 假既</blockquote><br />\n做咩?講黎聽下"},{"pid":"5cc9abec1cbacea47ab406fa58502be19f60ec4a","tid":171393,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好珍惜啦"},{"pid":"a305469a963cbb5aafc2dc5a1768ceb0cba8243f","tid":171393,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:21:14